---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
const title = "Let's Work Together"
const description = "Got a website that's not pulling its weight? Let's fix that."
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="contact-page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 class="page-title">Let's Work Together</h1>
      <p class="page-description">
        Your website should be making you money, not excuses.
      </p>
      <hr class="page-rule" />
    </header>

    <div class="contact-content">
      <div class="contact-info">
        <p>
          If your site is slow, invisible to Google, or confusing to customers, you've got a problem. I fix those problems with performance optimization, SEO strategy, and content that actually converts.
        </p>

        <h2>What I Work On</h2>
        <ul class="services-list">
          <li><strong>Full site builds</strong> for growing businesses that need it done right the first time</li>
          <li><strong>SEO audits</strong> that tell you what's actually wrong (not what some tool thinks might be wrong)</li>
          <li><strong>Performance overhauls</strong> for sites that load like it's 2010</li>
          <li><strong>Content strategy</strong> for businesses tired of guessing what works</li>
          <li><strong>Ongoing maintenance</strong> so your site doesn't become a liability</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          I don't take every project. If you're looking for cheap, fast, or someone who'll just nod along, I'm not your guy. But if you want honest advice and work that moves the needle, we should talk.
        </p>

        <h2>How This Works</h2>
        <ol class="process-list">
          <li>You reach out on Twitter or LinkedIn</li>
          <li>We have a real conversation about your business and what you actually need</li>
          <li>If it's a fit, I send you a proposal</li>
          <li>We get to work</li>
        </ol>

        <p>
          No endless discovery calls. No sales pitch. Just straight talk about whether I can help.
        </p>

        <h2>Find Me Online</h2>
        
        <div class="contact-links">
          <a href="https://x.com/kumawebco" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <span class="contact-label">Twitter/X</span>
            @kumawebco
            <span class="contact-note">Where I share unfiltered thoughts on web dev, SEO, and the state of the internet.</span>
          </a>
          
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/thegrantkennedy" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <span class="contact-label">LinkedIn</span>
            Grant Kennedy
            <span class="contact-note">The professional version of the same person.</span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <hr class="section-break" />

        <p class="not-ready">
          <strong>Not ready to reach out yet?</strong> Fair enough. Check out my <a href="/blog">blog</a> for the kind of advice I'd give you anyway.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .contact-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 8);
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-primary);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
  }

  .page-description {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .page-rule {
    height: 4px;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    border: none;
    width: 120px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .contact-content {
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .contact-info h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
    margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6);
  }

  .contact-info p {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
  }

  .services-list,
  .process-list {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
    margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
  }

  .services-list li,
  .process-list li {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 1.5);
  }

  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
    margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
  }

  .contact-link {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .contact-link:hover,
  .contact-link:focus {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .contact-label {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) / 2);
  }

  .contact-link:hover .contact-label,
  .contact-link:focus .contact-label {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .contact-note {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) / 2);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .section-break {
    height: 2px;
    background-color: var(--color-border);
    border: none;
    width: 100%;
    margin: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6) 0;
  }

  .not-ready {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .page-description {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
  }
</style>